The paper discusses the challenges and limitations of AI safety, which is a subfield of AI. Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves formal proofs and mathematical models, which are common in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.RO (Robotics), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Additionally, the paper discusses the impact of unpredictability on AI safety, which is related to software engineering and system design, making cs.SE a possible sub-category as well.
